                    "line_text": "-Yo soy cristiano... -Y ¿ama la pobreza?",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+-+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "-Tonto es quien la riqueza no prefiere.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "Yo soy cristiano... -¿A su enemigo quiere?",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++-+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
